| s_axi_control | IP_ISR       | 0x0c   | 32    | RW     | IP Interrupt Status Register     | 0=CHAN0_INT_ST 1=CHAN1_INT_ST                                        |
| s_axi_control | width        | 0x10   | 32    | W      | Data signal of width             |                                                                      |
| s_axi_control | height       | 0x18   | 32    | W      | Data signal of height            |                                                                      |
| s_axi_control | power_th     | 0x20   | 32    | W      | Data signal of power_th          |                                                                      |
| s_axi_control | strict       | 0x28   | 32    | W      | Data signal of strict            |                                                                      |
